{"tid":612690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區感激助鞏固香港仔票源","createTime":"2018-04-01T05:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T05:18:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"482a5572580640c663acdbd7ea156053603d896d","tid":612690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180401/20349038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180401%2F20349038&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1b67b78a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180401%2F20349038&h=afb9774d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180401/20349038</a><br />\n<br />\n區感激助鞏固香港仔票源<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180401/large/0323wai1001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180401%2Flarge%2F0323wai1001.jpg&h=e6d4e24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區諾軒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《蘋果》翻查選舉事務處的票站結果數字，發現區諾軒在多個楊森曾經協助拉票的香港仔區內多個票站，其得票都比新民黨陳家珮多；即使在「紅區」石排灣，區諾軒得票較陳家珮少，但仍然能獲得接近四成半選票。<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒感激老將楊森助選，對他在相關地區爭取長者街坊票有不少幫助。<br />\n<br />\n楊森在補選中，多次現身香港仔及石排灣為區諾軒拉票。選舉事務處資料顯示，區在香港仔中心、田灣邨、景惠花園以及逸港居的得票同樣比陳家珮多，其中在香港仔中心的得票更比陳多逾600票。陳家珮在石排灣邨得票雖比區諾軒多，但區的得票仍達近45%。區諾軒稱，楊森到訪香港仔和石排灣時，年長街坊反應特別好，相信能替他鞏固該區長者選民的支持。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t行動不便　婦受「感召」投票<br />\n要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t區諾軒勝選功臣楊森：受助街坊記得我<br />\n要聞 6小時前"},{"pid":"1e0c7b2ea08acbddd84269e04b20332b62400fcd","tid":612690,"uid":144869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"石排灣真係好多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:住緊"}]}